data.description: A brick beauty, updated and move-in ready!! This freshly painted,  3 bedroom 1.5 bath home offers a tiled living and dining room area with a galley kitchen.  New wall to wall carpet throughout bedrooms. The home also features a large bonus room with a bay window and laundry space. The HUGE backyard is perfect for entertaining.
